snippet.title: Kandinhale | Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Kandinhale is a story-driven short RPGMaker game in which you'll have to escape from the clutches of Kandinhale, the company that owns almost the entire consumables market in this idyllic Candy World.

✦ Estimated playtime: 30 minutes - 45 minutes
✦ Number of endings: 7
✦ Languages: English, Spanish (more languages might be available in the future).
